1 customer except under the terms of a tariff approved by the Utilities Commission in accordance
2 with G.S. 62-127.1.
3 SECTION 2.(c) The application required to be filed with the Utilities Commission
4 pursuant to G.S. 62-127.2, as enacted by subsection (a) of this section, shall be filed by the
5 electric public utility no later than 180 days after the effective date of this section.
6 SECTION 2.(d) This section is effective when it becomes law.
